content.text:
All three cards have exactly the same ruling date: 2004-10-04. The claim states that "Orcish Artillery has the earliest ruling date among Orcish Artillery, Aura of Silence, and Guerrilla Tactics, not the latest." Since all three cards share the same ruling date, Orcish Artillery does not have the earliest ruling date distinctly — it ties with all of them. It simultaneously has both the earliest and the latest date (since they're all the same). The claim asserts it has the earliest but "not the latest," which is contradicted since they all share the same date — it cannot have the earliest without also having the latest.
